<title>蔡徐坤被全网黑之后，要起诉B站，为啥黑蔡徐坤成了潮流？</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/2QhNVhTyml</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/2QhNVhTyml</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;107&quot; data-backw=&quot;622&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xB6drHCHf6jSBSTyMI9yYWHeKg4PoomhNITJria8jEvlShAOODFNibic8rALMWVrCRzr1pedflfuEoIw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCHG4DAlzIdiaOr67pmCia7mhZW6leCibdfx9jtjPUALDcVq7Lptib1RIAfR2hs6vDW6cUODHwWqic8h0w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.1719939117199391&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCHG4DAlzIdiaOr67pmCia7mhZW6leCibdfx9jtjPUALDcVq7Lptib1RIAfR2hs6vDW6cUODHwWqic8h0w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;657&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;436&quot; data-backw=&quot;654&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlxTYKjeRia0Or7ibRJratHWoQPTHQicEeyuRI4UWnSCicEx80k2r9hXTPwg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6666666666666666&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlxTYKjeRia0Or7ibRJratHWoQPTHQicEeyuRI4UWnSCicEx80k2r9hXTPwg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;657&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.44711538461538464&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlxTRIEAibIXmBBichEVYicPfSbJw5GnbpxrXLh6HMrjsc2x5A0os2cAEyw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;624&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot;&gt;被全网黑的蔡徐坤要开始维权了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;说实话，作为一个大龄姨母，我对蔡徐坤不关注。我周围的同事和朋友，也对蔡徐坤比较无感。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;但我们都知道有一种和他有关的全网共识叫：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;讨厌蔡徐坤&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5603603603603604&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NloAHL5yWMibg93CQp4qUhhwjniaAC9kXBRXnOrf3AQSaEKWiaSzeORPLCA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;555&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：bilibili&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;昨天，蔡徐坤粉丝团官微发微博点名B站，&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;称&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“蔡徐坤/给B站/发律师函”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlPicibjQiaopd04yRODWpmkrgfviaCSOgFLge8dKT6vQ4IIs8O8SDAMMBmA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlMrHfXJJibtqmP4trR7RYsLxWnJBmnRS3W7gUZiboumLL6udSQyv0ica7A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6747826086956522&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlPicibjQiaopd04yRODWpmkrgfviaCSOgFLge8dKT6vQ4IIs8O8SDAMMBmA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;575&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;蔡徐坤的代理律师指责B站上存在有关蔡徐坤大量&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;辱骂暴力血腥&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;的内容。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;并且还暗示这些内容已经触犯了《民发总则》、《民法通则》和《刑法》。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;如果该站再不删除侵权内容，将追究侵权者的法律责任。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;925&quot; data-backw=&quot;654&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;blob:https://mp.weixin.qq.com/7296aa8b-f51a-4ad6-8e89-76d021a5ffb1&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlAKzpibJzUJVLHGveNOGn3GDQjCcpBxF301rSAPOqhL3sHTOZ46Y5jQg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;1080&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;130.45871559633028&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;1527.5229357798166&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2944444444444445&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlUzrVB5GRaw5FYD6V632TowHusnjWeeBGWNlohto8YNlXpDnXlw627w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;当晚， B站也做出官方回应。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;191&quot; data-backw=&quot;588&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlVLrDEibIPib3lPIKQC1PibDakweCtHlOX2iaSBQxYWjyRu1Luoa5Wey1iag/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlFmJP4j6TRNH1OdWzE1fwBT3de8b3iaAhHzghEOvHlndLWNebN8ahkhQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.32482993197278914&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlFmJP4j6TRNH1OdWzE1fwBT3de8b3iaAhHzghEOvHlndLWNebN8ahkhQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;588&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;最后，B站还推荐了一篇人民网的文章&lt;strong&gt;《看舆论监督中“公众人物”的名誉权问题》&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这条推荐阅读确实耐人寻味。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;文章的内容是关于发生在2002年中国足球队队员范志毅因上海《东方体育日报》登载他涉嫌赌球的报道，状告文汇新民联合报业集团侵犯名誉权&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;的审判结果。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;法院一审判决：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;对范志毅的诉讼请求不予支持&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;B站是否在暗示”我不害怕，告吧，但是看起来你好像赢不了“呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;蔡徐坤维权已经不是第一次了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;今年3月，蔡徐坤工作室就发出严正声明，将对蓄意抹黑的行为取证，备诉。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;924&quot; data-backw=&quot;654&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlPmCuLvSWmLCy6BLp0FSKqMOoqT8DYpGZsyWzx4k3Jicoo5IKdmpIoZg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlPmCuLvSWmLCy6BLp0FSKqMOoqT8DYpGZsyWzx4k3Jicoo5IKdmpIoZg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;689.9999999999999&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;133.99082568807341&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;793.3944954128441&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9550724637681159&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NluxDYLLdsTtMicnlJjvurgqq2XlPazbLnTwiaYdI7PnGt4kDv8DoOMCIg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;690&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：搜狐&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;通过“偶像练习生”C位出道的蔡徐坤，可以说是当下中国第一流量担当，粉丝无数。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;靠流量蹿红，毁誉参半肯定是意料之中。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;我看了看，网上关于蔡徐坤的负面评价确实很多。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;有人说：&lt;strong&gt;你们不觉得黑他黑得太残忍了吗？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;他才不到20岁啊。。。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;一直以来，我对于这种说辞比较不屑一顾。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;既然选择站在人群中间，就要承受飞来的刀子。是生是死，各凭本事了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;本人不是蔡徐坤的粉，也不是B站粉，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但看了B站上的一些视频后，老姨母也觉得蔡徐坤真的有点惨。。。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;171&quot; data-backw=&quot;654&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;blob:https://mp.weixin.qq.com/c03e6888-5b80-4188-9594-915a59def265&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.26132930513595165&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77Nl5aZ2vibZj6QG0qliaAYI0ZsAV3vfAho0ed3TUpOpHj3fs5AHfiaickgWPg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;662&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; simsun=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;说到底，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; simsun=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;蔡徐坤做得最错的一件事就是做了NBA新春贺岁形象大使&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; simsun=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;559&quot; data-backw=&quot;654&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlcyO5ibxgrfQfT6H6fMNHsWibseDRlYv5lvCTrrtY3WHeIicp7voQiaM5Uw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlcyO5ibxgrfQfT6H6fMNHsWibseDRlYv5lvCTrrtY3WHeIicp7voQiaM5Uw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;683&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;542.01376146789&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7935578330893118&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCwKoic31DIAaTKNoia1z77NlkqDlMZhvOAwQFppBgnqm7gKwugGFia0Jk68nz6azg8IW0EsAASs68bg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;683&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; simsun=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; left=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;得知这一消息后，虎扑上无数人直接选择死亡。。。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

